  "base_commit": "dfae37195bed15dce84af0b17ef04cdc3704ef5e",
  "pr_number": 4974,
  "issue_number": 4973,
  "issue_title": "`z.core.File` is incompatible with `globalThis.File` type",
  "issue_body": "It looks like `z.core.File` changes added in v4.0.6 are not compatible with `globalThis.File`.\n\nLooks like it's because the `size` and `type` properties in `z.core.File` are mutable, but are readonly in `globalThis.File`.\n\n[Repro](https://stackblitz.com/edit/zod-file-bug-repro?file=test%2Frepro.test.ts)\n\n```typescript\nimport { expectTypeOf, test } from 'vitest'\nimport * as z from 'zod'\n\ntest('repro', () => {\n  const file = new File([], 'test.txt')\n  expectTypeOf(z.file().parse(file)).toEqualTypeOf(file)\n  //                                               \ud801\ude58__\ud801\ude58 not equal because `size` and `type` are mutable\n})\n```\n\nShould be a quick fix, will open a PR in a few",
  "merged_at": "2025-07-25T00:09:09Z",
